data.description: Attractive brick Raised Ranch is located on a beautiful tree lined block. The home features a large living room, three bedrooms. and a full semi finished basement with bath. Great shopping, transportation and schools are nearby. This home is priced to sell!! Lot/room sizes estimated. Cash offers require a minimum 10% earnest money deposit. See attached mold and structure disclosures and Point of Sale Inspection. Buyer must comply with the Calumet Park as is transfer requirements. This property is subject to a 3-Day First Look Period. Seller will negotiate offers after the period expires.
